All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable, Iterable<V>, Collection<V>, Set<V>
public class IndexedHashSet<K,V>
extends HashSet<V>

A data structure to store unique values indexed by a given key. If an item added is found to duplicate an existing object, the object is not added and no index is assigned.
